        "label": "1Password Events API bearer token",
        "generateUrl": "https://start.1password.com/integrations/directory",
        "setup": "In a 1Password Business account, [sign in](https://start.1password.com/signin), open [Integrations Directory](https://start.1password.com/integrations/directory), choose an Events Reporting integration (or **Other**), create it, then issue a bearer token. Save the token when prompted; 1Password notes it is shown once and can be saved as an API Credential item. You can also mint one from the CLI with [`op events-api create`](https://www.1password.dev/cli/reference/management-commands/events-api).",
