        "setup": "Register as a 1Password partner via the [1Password Partner Program](https://1password.com/partnerships) or contact the partnerships team as directed in the [Partnership API reference](https://www.1password.dev/partnership-api/reference/). Registered partners are granted bearer tokens for the billing servers.",
